      "blocks": {
        "rich_text_WKPpUb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Heading",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h1>The Best Jewelry for Active Women: Style Meets Performance</h1>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "follow_us_y3zhkb": {
          "type": "follow_us",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Follow Us on"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_dDtEpm": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Jewelry has always been about more than just decoration, it’s about self-expression, memories, and sometimes, a quiet confidence. For women constantly in motion, between workouts, deadlines, errands, and travel, the jewelry needs to do more than sparkle.</p><p>The answer? Choosing pieces designed with both style and practicality in mind. Jewelry shouldn’t just look pretty; it should move with you.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_8dMhVk": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Makes Jewelry Suitable for an Active Lifestyle?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>What Makes Jewelry Suitable for an Active Lifestyle?</h2><p>While most people think jewelry is not suitable for an active lifestyle, if your jewelry is designed right, you can wear it everywhere, be it at the gym or for hiking. Here's what separates ordinary pieces from those that truly work for active wearers:</p>",
            "custom_id": "suitable-jewelry"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_64mQcL": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/New_Project.jpg",
            "text": "<h3>1. Comfort in Motion</h3><p>If a ring causes callouses when lifting or your earring gets stuck in your hair when you’re running around taking care of your child, that’s a sign the piece isn’t working for your lifestyle. <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/sports-collection\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Active-friendly jewelry</span></a> needs to sit in-line against the body, without edges or parts that catch, poke, or move too much.</p><h3>2. Secure Construction</h3><p>Your jewelry should stay where it belongs. That means clasps that don’t pop open, earrings that don’t fall out, and stones that stay put. Whether you’re out for a jog or reaching for groceries, you shouldn’t have to worry about losing something valuable.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_PDhTB7": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Low Maintenance, High Durability",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>3. Low Maintenance, High Durability</h3><p>Everyday wear brings exposure to sweat, sunscreen, soap, and impact. The best jewelry for active women resists tarnishing and holds up well with minimal upkeep. Materials like 14k or 18k Gold, Platinum Setting, and Lab Grown diamonds score high here, not just for their appearance, but for their longevity.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ndVTQi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Jewelry Styles That Don’t Hold You Back",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Jewelry Styles That Don’t Hold You Back</h2><p>The goal isn’t to stop wearing jewelry, it’s to wear it smarter. Below are styles and types that many women find blend seamlessly into even the most hands-on routines.</p>",
            "custom_id": "jewelry-styles"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_cEizxU": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Bezel Set Rings: Built for Movement",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Lucira_product_46535_ef3c7bb5-e036-406e-a807-dfc2e3be49a8.jpg",
            "text": "<h3>Bezel Set Rings: Built for Movement</h3><p>Rings can be tricky. If they have raised stones or sharp prongs, they can catch on fabric, gym equipment, or even hair. That’s why Bezel Settings have become a favorite among those who live actively.</p><p>Instead of holding the diamond in place with prongs, Bezel Settings encircle the stone entirely, locking it in securely. This not only protects the diamond but also reduces snagging. They're sleek, modern, and made for movement.</p><p>Want even more comfort? Choose a low-profile band that hugs the finger and won’t shift or spin throughout the day.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_hr4rCj": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Studs and Huggies: Earrings That Stay Put",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Lucira_product_46382.jpg",
            "text": "<h3>Studs and Huggies: Earrings That Stay Put</h3><p>Long dangles and oversized hoops may look dramatic, but they’re not practical if you’re constantly in motion. The better option? <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/studs\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Stud earrings</span></a> or <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/hoops\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">huggie hoops</span></a>, small pieces that sit close to the ear and don’t swing or pull.</p><p>Whether you’re tying your hair back, wearing a helmet, or slipping on a scarf, these styles stay comfortably in place. And with designs available in diamonds, minimal metals, or sleek shapes, you don’t have to sacrifice personality for practicality.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_Y34GAy": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Streamlined Necklaces: Subtle, Functional, and Strong",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Lucira_product_46561_596fbfc4-93a6-496c-829a-427d0cb8f7b9.jpg",
            "text": "<h3>Streamlined Necklaces: Subtle, Functional, and Strong</h3><p>For necklaces, think simplicity. Thin, lightweight chains with small, centered pendants are ideal. If the pendant is heavy or the chain too long, it may swing or tangle—not exactly helpful mid-yoga pose or on a crowded metro.</p><p>Look for:</p><ul><li>Flat-link chains that sit against the skin</li><li>Strong clasps (like lobster locks) that won’t give out unexpectedly</li><li>Designs that layer easily under clothing without discomfort</li></ul><p>Avoid chunky statement pieces if you’re going to be moving a lot. They’re great for events, but less so for everyday hustle.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_ccKET6": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Bracelets That Don’t Interrupt Your Flow",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Lucira_product_46594_e5511c33-1114-4f8b-ae4f-e90cab6a26b3.jpg",
            "text": "<h3>Bracelets That Don’t Interrupt Your Flow</h3><p>Bracelets can be the most challenging when it comes to active wear. Charm bracelets or bangles that jingle constantly may not feel comfortable, especially when typing, writing, or lifting.</p><p>Instead, go for:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/tennis-bracelets\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Tennis Bracelets</span></a> with flexible links</li><li><a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/cuff-bracelets\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Cuff Bracelets</span></a> with a snug fit</li><li>Minimalist designs with secure, flat clasps</li></ul><p>If you’re someone who likes wearing a fitness watch or smart band, look for pieces that won’t clash or tangle with your wearable tech.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_t89GTB": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Jewelry That Moves the Way You Do",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/New_Project_1.jpg",
            "text": "<h2>Jewelry That Moves the Way You Do</h2><p>You don’t need to take your jewelry off every time you break a sweat. You just need people who understand how your life works.</p><p>Whether you're a cyclist, a traveler, a mother, or simply someone who values ease, jewelry should feel like a part of you, not a distraction. Designs that are thoughtful, secure, and strong give you the freedom to live fully without leaving beauty behind.</p><p>Because elegance doesn’t belong only in quiet, still moments. Sometimes, it shows up in motion.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "jewelry-in-motion",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        }
      },
